        {
            "level": "H3",
            "text": "Lead time is the length of time between when a forecast is output and the occurrence of the",
            "page": 4
        },
        {
            "level": "H3",
            "text": "shock that was forecasted. It is unclear the impact that forecast running time has on lead times",
            "page": 4
        },
        {
            "level": "H3",
            "text": "for implementation. In the case of Typhoon Ursula (Phanfone) in 2019, the trigger was reached",
